OL,3,CPolice believe missing Piper Alpha
OL,4,Chero has been swept out into the North
OL,5,CSea
OL,7,FA missing man, who helped to save
OL,8,Flives in the Piper Alpha oil rig
OL,9,Fdisaster in 1988, is believed to have
OL,10,Fgone into water off the Northumberland
OL,11,Fcoast, Northumbria Police have said.
OL,13,FThe force has been carrying out
OL,14,Fextensive enquiries to try and trace
OL,15,Fmissing 78-year-old Charles Yarwood,
OL,16,Fwho is known as Mike to his family and
OL,17,Ffriends, for the last two months.
