OL,3,CPolice believe missing Piper Alpha
OL,4,Chero has been swept out into the North
OL,5,CSea
OL,7,FHe was last seen in the Amble area of
OL,8,FNorthumberland on the night of Friday
OL,9,F21 November 2025, but in an update
OL,10,Fthis morning (Friday 23 January),
OL,11,Fpolice have said they now believe Mike
OL,12,Fentered the water near one of the
OL,13,Fpiers in Amble and has been swept
OL,14,Ffurther out into the North Sea.
OL,16,FThey have said his next of kin have
OL,17,Fbeen informed and are being supported
OL,18,Fby officers at this difficult time.
