OL,12,FDetective Inspector Calum Meikle from
OL,13,FNorthumbria Police said: "This is an
OL,14,Fextremely tragic incident, and our
OL,15,Fthoughts are very much with Mike's
OL,16,Floved ones at this time.
OL,18,F"Our officers continue to support his
OL,19,Ffamily and we would ask that their
OL,20,Fprivacy is respected.
