OL,5,CSea
OL,7,F"Extensive enquiries have been ongoing
OL,8,Fsince concerns were raised for Mike,
OL,9,Fincluding deploying specialist teams
OL,10,Fto search for him."
OL,12,FA wide range of police resources have
OL,13,Fbeen used in the search for Mike,
OL,14,Fincluding officers from the Force's
OL,15,FMarine Unit, the National Police Air
OL,16,FService, the Dog Section and Drone
OL,17,FUnit.
