OL,7,FMeanwhile, volunteers from the HM
OL,8,FCoastguard and Mountain Rescue, RNLI
OL,9,Fand the Civil Air Service, along with
OL,10,FMike's family and friends, have also
OL,11,Fbeen involved in the search.
OL,13,FMike became known as a local hero
OL,14,Fafter he helped to save lives
OL,15,Ffollowing the world's worst off-shore
OL,16,Foil industry disaster in 1988, when
OL,17,Fthe North Sea oil platform, the Piper
OL,18,FAlpha, exploded off the coast of
OL,19,FAberdeen.
