OL,7,F167 people were killed in the tragedy,
OL,8,Fincluding 17 from the North East.
OL,10,FMike was a winchman for RAF Boulmer at
OL,11,Fthe time, and helped to save some of
OL,12,Fthe lives of those who were caught up
OL,13,Fin the inferno.
